ygData.messageBody:
Timowear wrote:
"Hi, I just did a search for gay groups within EQ, wondering if there
is one, and well.. I found this one :)"

Hehehe...actually you found at least *three* for the price of one search!
Andy's guild, Mystic Alliance on Rodcet, Nameless Love on The Nameless
(http://www.sweetvision.com/~namelesslove/index.shtml), and the Bears guild,
Ordo Ursi Prismatus on Lanys T'Vyll (http://ordo.darke.net).

Which begs a question - does anyone know of a lesbian guild? I had a Family
member ask me in-game the other night if I knew of any womyn's guilds in EQ,
and I didn't know of any. I pointed her to this list, but I've not heard of
any.

Happy hunting, and welcome to EQRainbow!


Jack
Ordo Ursi Prismatus
Field Officer and Swiss Army Knife (Shaman)
